            ">Bitcoin record</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-dec-7-1.jpg" alt="Bitcoin record" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Bitcoin has just hit a huge milestone, crossing the <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cqj0wkwv1x2o" target="_blank">$100,000</a> mark for the first time. The surge in price has been fueled by President Donald Trump's new policies that <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/business/markets/trump-claims-credit-bitcoin-reaches-100000-crypto-policies-rcna182994" target="_blank">support</a> cryptocurrency. The price reached this milestone when Trump announced his plan to nominate <a href="https://apnews.com/article/sec-chair-atkins-gensler-investors-financial-markets-d1c544f1846071b33c75b9f2dd0c1ba4" target="_blank">Paul Atkins</a>, a known crypto supporter, to lead the Securities and Exchange Commission.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">This spike in Bitcoin’s value highlights its importance in the vast $3.3 trillion digital asset market. Since the U.S. election, Bitcoin’s value has <a href="https://abcnews.go.com/Business/bitcoin-races-past-100000-dollars-fueled-post-election-rally/story?id=116127616#:~:text=Bitcoin%20has%20climbed%20more%20than%2040%25%20since%20Election,period%2C%20while%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq%20has%20jumped%202.6%25." target="_blank">jumped</a> by 40%. The president-elect has promised to make the U.S. “the crypto-capital of the planet,” a stark deviation from his 2021 stand where he called crypto a scam.</p>
        </mj-text>
