              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Hunter pardoned</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">President Joe Biden’s decision to <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/12/02/politics/hunter-biden-pardon-analysis/index.html" target="_blank">pardon</a> his son, Hunter Biden, sparked political and legal controversy by blurring the lines between politics and justice in the United States. The pardon clears Hunter of <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/06/11/politics/hunter-biden-gun-trial-verdict/index.html" target="_blank">charges</a> related to gun possession and tax evasion, marking a departure from Biden's earlier stance of <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/joe-biden/biden-says-will-not-pardon-son-hunter-biden-convicted-gun-related-char-rcna155920" target="_blank">not interfering</a> in his son's legal matters.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="0px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
     <!-- Content sections -->
